Essential:
	build-essential
	autoconf
	libtool

If documentation is needed:
	doxygen
	dot (for diagrams)

Prepare tools:
	./autogen.sh
	./configure CXXFLAGS='-g0 -O3'
	or
	./configure CXXFLAGS='-g3 -O0' for debelopment

then compile with:
	make
